reviewText: I had this when I was a kid, but I watched it so much, I wore it out. Now, I'm an adult and I have it again, if only for the nostalgia. So glad I saved the VCR. The tape I recieved looked exactly like the one I had. Right down to the worn box. Do yourself a favor, if you love monster trucks, pulling tractors, or anything with 4 wheels and a motor, get this today.
